{
  "texts": [
    "This dataset is collected from the 2018 edition of the Yelp Challenge.",
    "3 We utilize local businesses' Categories, City and Stars as attributes.",
    "We employ the 10-core setting to ensure a minimum of ten interactions for each user and item.",
    "For each dataset, we organize users' interactions chronologically based on timestamps, allowing us to create the corresponding historical interaction sequences.",
    "Items are described using their product IDs&Names."
  ]
}